55:05.600 --> 55:08.769
That black little rat
you used to hang out with.

55:08.771 --> 55:11.339
Got stretched three days ago.

55:12.474 --> 55:15.341
I hear they had to
winch him up twice.

55:15.343 --> 55:17.745
Twitching and frothing
